RACE.FOOTNOTES: FORITTABLE broke inwards, bumped FAVORITE LIGHT, pressed outside early, forced issue turn, dueled between horses into stretch, was bumped by GOING SUCCESS drifting in twice in early stretch, took a short lead, drifted out into that rival through the stretch and carried that same rival out in late stretch while holding on. GOING SUCCESS stalked forced pace outside, challenged stretch, came in and bumped FORITTABLE in early stretch, gave best trying to get by that drifting out rival but was carried out further and bothered late. OH MAN OH MAN stalked off rail, rallied for show. FAVORITE LIGHT stumbled at the break, was bumped by FORITTABLE and in turn bumped with BOLD NEW TRICKS, moved to the lead inside under increasing pressure, dueled into stretch, gave best before giving way in mid stretch. BOLD NEW TRICKS, bumped at the break, trailed to stretch, rallied belatedly. G B'S TURBO stalked forced pace inside, lacked rally. THIRSTY EARS stalked forced pace between horses, dropped back turn, faded. The rider aboard GOING SUCCESS lodged a claim of foul against the rider of FORITTABLE for interference in deep stretch. As a result, FORITTABLE was disqualified and placed second.
